{"tid":1936338,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好鄰舍北區教會請人啊","createTime":"2020-03-21T07:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T03:26:48.000Z","uid":295793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3dd4a6439742de505efdbac58cd0ccbec19225","tid":1936338,"uid":295793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2249241785370184?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1561265357501167%2Fposts%2F2249241785370184%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F0wAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=71365fba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2249241785370184?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會誠聘<br />\n青少年幹事（數名，可申請全職或半職）<br />\n<br />\n1.認同本會理念<br />\n2.熱衷追求在香港實踐愛、公義、謙卑<br />\n3.為理想拼搏、為香港付出<br />\n4.高中程度或同等學歷以上較佳<br />\n5.重視團隊合作<br />\n6.熟悉中英文打字、懂文宣圖設計、多媒體設計、電子產品及音樂、能即時上班優先<br />\n<br />\n工作內容：<br />\n教會事務協助、當值、基本文宣。出勤：接觸有需要的人；統籌義工；活動設計及帶領。<br />\n<br />\n每週上班時數為24（半職）/44（全職）小時，返兩晚夜，輪班輪休，或有需要按個別活動調整上班時間。工作地點為北區或觀塘區。<br />\n<br />\n薪金約為每月$6500-7500（此為半職，全職約14000左右），視乎資歷及工作經驗而定，合約為期半年，若半年眾籌成功，表現理想則可續約。<br />\n<br />\n應徵者請於4月3日前 將個人履歷、應徵信email :egowonggnnd@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n本會使命︰<br />\n「讓社區改變 還基層光明<br />\n成為別人鄰舍 以愛轉化北區」<br />\n<br />\n本會經訓︰「世人哪，耶和華已指示你何為善。他向你所要的是什麼呢？只要你行公義，好憐憫，存謙卑的心，與你的神同行。」 ( 彌迦書6:8 )"},{"pid":"5069a67b3ee42aa691ff66078b47aecc72061706","tid":1936338,"uid":154223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d33e564839ea07ba95c84b84d7ffebba771750","tid":1936338,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捐埋好鄰舍有得退稅"},{"pid":"16825edd92fcac294ec45d05ed5377fc04515303","tid":1936338,"uid":290739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4745aaaa041e895d91c4b26802ff939d38996412","tid":1936338,"uid":316990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:26:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}